{"tid":629653,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"認真問 清潔工人究竟有冇做垃圾分類？","createTime":"2018-04-15T01:11:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-15T06:42:51.000Z","uid":147499,"like":19,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"bbcb98aa5e070cbeffa00aee8ae8a97c2e0f8899","tid":629653,"uid":147499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T01:11:02.000Z","msg":"搭巴士嘅時候見到一個有分類標示嘅垃圾桶<br />\n當時有清潔工人係度倒垃圾<br />\n咁啱巴士等紅燈，我咪無聊望望<br />\n<br />\n個清潔工人拎左個大膠袋<br />\n將廢紙果格拉出黎<br />\n然後連袋同垃圾一嘢塞入大膠袋<br />\n如是者 第二格都係咁<br />\n但到第三格嘅時候<br />\n佢唔再係袋連垃圾咁塞<br />\n而係將第三格嘅垃圾直接倒落大膠袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實香港有冇法例係指定要做垃圾分類？<br />\n相關程序又係點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果冇，咁擺咁多垃圾分類桶做乜？"},{"pid":"64d8c7ba7abf8fd06319b66b3257a9aa8c99dc0d","tid":629653,"uid":53629,"like":11,"dislike":3,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T01:20:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8e76f1fd6ca6e8c6b3bbb81e928b45974c93e32a","tid":629653,"uid":120955,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T01:21:47.000Z","msg":"唔會 ，因為根本冇判到回收公司"},{"pid":"9cc98f1f2a22763f118b7835e23fe29b025c23e7","tid":629653,"uid":53429,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T01:22:12.000Z","msg":"梗係無啦, 我公司不嬲都係擺番去垃圾堆度,<br />\n你話報紙就話唔定可以同你草下,<br />\n其他D又重體積又大梗係去垃圾堆到啦"},{"pid":"34f53e749a12a59bfe604ab075b653c2f108ca3f","tid":629653,"uid":130901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T01:37:09.000Z","msg":"暫時分類只係益公司阿姐賣紙皮"},{"pid":"55a72a0c9587ac130b82861be935e727d0efcb8b","tid":629653,"uid":109983,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T01:38:18.000Z","msg":"冇 做下樣"},{"pid":"e115f8b6287b04ad74638eddd66c2d93cc2e04bd","tid":629653,"uid":50744,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime"